%h1 Regions#index
.container.region-container
  .row.wrap-div-region
    - @regions.each do |region|
      .col-md-4
        .hovereffect
          = link_to (image_tag region.image,  class:"img-responsive-region"), region
          = link_to region do
            .overlay
              .region-title
                = region.name
